The Children’s Investment Fund Management (UK) LLP (TCI) Selects Charles River Development to Automate Compliance Operations


Boston, London, Melbourne, Paris and Singapore – 27 February 2007












										Charles River Development, an award-winning provider of financial software and services to the global investment management community, today announced that The Childrenâs Investment Fund Management (UK) LLP (TCI), one of Europeâs most prominent hedge fund managers, has selected the Charles River Investment Management System to support its compliance operations. Charles River now helps over 240 investment firms in 30 countries worldwide, including 60 clients in Europe, the Middle East and Africa, manage their front- and middle-office operations.

										Risk Management Systems







